{"tid":1776403,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"龍格堡初試勝感","createTime":"2019-12-09T13:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T10:15:07.000Z","uid":19552,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f22d53103705f565a2182f1914665d97ec26f0a1","tid":1776403,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:39:57.000Z","msg":"凌晨4點上演 大家請較定鬧鐘睇"},{"pid":"9d55d55cba5abc52ea82f17bfa4a53c91c41104f","tid":1776403,"uid":216828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d0015540be6bd9ca486232fcc533cbff65b9ae0","tid":1776403,"uid":10014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:41:06.000Z","msg":"屌你 又燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77cdfed225b18dddccf5d5753f8e40db5f268216","tid":1776403,"uid":81052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:42:12.000Z","msg":"食屎啦瀨屎蓋<br />\n龍蛇有咩得罪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0557d2b0fc102f59cd92b6412b93e34015501244","tid":1776403,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:42:43.000Z","msg":"認真西咸今季咁柒阿狗唔會輸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8428962fa810a7e7dc30a5957b03dbb2959efb4","tid":1776403,"uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:43:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmKV2z6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmKV2z6.jpg&h=241aee25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有班教育界痴線佬為左唔比學生落入聖誕節圈套<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776399</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n昨日遊行最深刻的一句「初夏&mdash;&mdash;寒冬」<br />\n我們不經不覺由初夏走到冬天<br />\n由撐黃色食店走到黃色經濟圈<br />\n香港人就是有心有力也有財力<br />\n<br />\n講返正題，以往每年聖誕聯歡/Re-U都總係會叫啲最方便快捷嘅KFC、PizzaHut聖誕套餐，今年相信大家都不了不了，所以我地整合左所有會做到會服務嘅黃店，大家識Do啦！<br />\n*（亦建議學生會將圖印出派比同學宣傳📃）<br />\n<br />\n最後，教育同行全體祝大家有個Yellow Christmas 🎄💛<br />\n<br />\n*我地已盡量向店方直接確認到會服務，但始終人手有限，資料未必齊全，歡迎各位Comment報料。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTg: <a href=\"https://t.me/hkteacher\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkteacher&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F4eonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=d4a3e18a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkteacher</a><br />\nFb: shorturl.at/kqtJM<br />\nIg: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/standbyeducatorshk?igshid=juzv8s7rtxb5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fstandbyeducatorshk%3Figshid%3Djuzv8s7rtxb5&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F4eonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=2f583c52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/standbyeducatorshk?igshid=juzv8s7rtxb5</a>"},{"pid":"58d6ec5c554e2154f38c301cd116d8b6fac2f36a","tid":1776403,"uid":47149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6259f7850ed28669068b06d5f7e29ad9d13033e","tid":1776403,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0557d2b0fc102f59cd92b6412b93e34015501244","tid":1776403,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:42:43.000Z","msg":"認真西咸今季咁柒阿狗唔會輸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:46:05.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"9e06e5cfb6cd108feb3f3ae61600fbffb42dbab2","tid":1776403,"uid":151324,"l